results.title: Life Laugh Love Sign
results.description:
Live, Laugh, Love
Classic motto for your home. Display your philosophy for all to see!

Why go with Carved Wood:
This sign is uniquely hand crafted to create a warm and inviting atmosphere.  A carved piece of wood has changing depths that instantly stand out in any environment.  A piece like this will catch the eye of any guest.  This sign is a great way for you to add character to a room.   
Carved wood has a natural elegance that cannot be found in a two dimensional printed picture.  Pictures will fade over time but carved wood will not.  You and those you love will be able to enjoy the words on this sign for many pleasant years to come.
 
Caring for the Product:
This piece is made of pine, a naturally softwood.  The product has a single stain applied prior to engraving.  This accents the engravings.  Additional stain or protective coating can be applied.  

How was this made:
Proudly designed and crafted in our home-based shop in beautiful Yakima Washington.
The wood used in each piece is specifically selected for size and grain.  The wood is then sanded and stained by hand in preparation for engraving. To begin the engraving process the wood must be precisely positioned and secured into our jig. The CNC machine then accurately etches the design into the wood. From start to finish, it can take up to five days to make these unique and individually crafted pieces.
A video of the engraving process can be viewed here:  
For more custom decor, check out our Etsy shop!
Like us on Facebook! https://www.facebook.com/nwcarLLC/ and Instagram https://www.instagram.com/northwestcarving/
Thanks for shopping with us!!!
Todd & Jonathan
Owner - Northwest Carving and Routing
